author: wmtan
body:
This trivial pull request fixes the unit test in FWCore/Integration.
Someone modified edmPluginDump to add the module type to the output.
This broke the test of edmPluginDump in FWCore/Integration. because the output is compared with a "txt" file of the expected output.
This request simply corrects the expected output to be consistent with the modified edmPluginDump.
title: Fix expected output
